Package: plotarium
Title: Interactive ggplot2 figure builder
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2025-11-08
Authors@R: person("Oliver", "Schappacher", email = "git-oliver@web.de", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0008-6323-4417"))
Description: Plotarium is an interactive ggplot2 GUI that helps create figures. This package contains an RStudio addin to launch the app.
